the way she did...

413
00:53:34,144 --> 00:53:37,113
if she was fat or dark,
you'd be in trouble!

414
00:53:37,314 --> 00:53:38,941
Ronnie, you only go by
physical appearances?

415
00:53:39,149 --> 00:53:42,448
