not looking at the other one at all

416
00:53:42,652 --> 00:53:45,382
Who... Pooja?
- Pooja? Who's Pooja?

417
00:53:45,989 --> 00:53:50,187
Pooja is our childhood friend
- You really had some childhood

418
00:53:50,660 --> 00:53:52,525
Tina on one side
and Pooja on the other!

419
00:53:56,333 --> 00:53:58,198
So tell me how was she,
this childhood friend?

420
00:54:00,337 --> 00:54:04,637
She knows me so well...
she knows what I like to eat...

421
00:54:05,342 --> 00:54:07,139
she loves Hindi songs
just like me

422
00:54:09,679 --> 00:54:13,547
Pooja? I thought
you were talking about Tina

423
